cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.RO 

This paper is about object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves using a cascade structure to improve the performance of region proposal networks, which requires machine learning techniques such as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.LG). The authors also mention using a loss function and backpropagation, which are common techniques in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper focuses on real-world object detection, which involves robotics and automation (cs.RO).
